    • getToggleSwitchPos

      public ToggleSwitch getToggleSwitchPos()
      Method that returns the position of the toggle switch. Could be TYPED (that means tank parameters are set manually or RANDOM (that means tank parameteres are random values).
      Returns:
      toggle switch position

    • setModelValues

      public void setModelValues(String[] args)
      Method for setting values in model object. Designed to take the input directly from main() parameters.
      Parameters:
      args - string arguments from main() parameters. Should be in following order: tank base radius [m], initial fluid level height [m], initial IN1 input stream flow value [l/min], initial IN2 input stream flow value [l/min], initial OUT output stream flow value [l/min].

    • setModelValueIn1

      public void setModelValueIn1(double currentIn1LMin) throws InvalidArgumentException
      Wrapper method for setting IN1 value in model object.
      Parameters:
      currentIn1LMin - IN1 stream flow value [l/min]
      Throws:
      InvalidArgumentException - when parameter is out of range.
